Package Server.IndexStorageBarrel.Operations

Class BarrelRetriever

java.lang.Object
Server.IndexStorageBarrel.Operations.BarrelRetriever
public class BarrelRetriever extends Object
The BarrelRetriever class is responsible for retrieving data from the database related to website crawling and indexing.
